  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add beef strips and cook until browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Remove beef from skillet and set aside.",
    "Add bell peppers and onions to skillet and cook until tender, about 4-5 minutes.",
    "Add savory stir-fry sauce and Jamaican jerk seasoning to skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Return beef to skillet and stir to coat with sauce.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until sauce has thickened.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
